      • UserMatch

        public UserMatch​(int matchwith,
                 int matchtype,
                 String matchvalue)
          throws NumberFormatException
        Creates a new instance of UserMatch.
        Parameters:
        matchwith - determines which field i userdata table to match with.
        matchtype - determines how to match the field. SubjectDN fields can only be matched with 'begins with'.
        matchvalue - the value to match with.
        Throws:
        NumberFormatException - if matchvalue contains illegal numbervalue when matching number field.
